Instruction template for quick replies: Quick replies are an 
array, can have 1-11. Payload isn't really necessary with
quick_replies but the tag is still required.
<!--==============================-->

<response>
    <text_qr>
        <text>__messageText</text>
        <quick_replies>
            <content_type>text</content_type>
            <title>__qr1Text</title>
            <payload />
        </quick_replies>
        <quick_replies>
            <content_type>text</content_type>
            <title>__qr2Text</title>
            <payload />
        </quick_replies>
    </text_qr>
</response>